The vendored copy of upstream sources lives in `upstream/` of this repository
and is preserved verbatim from the upstream tag pinned in `UPSTREAM.lock`.
Upstream license texts inside `upstream/` are kept intact.

The transformed/rebranded distribution under `dist/` is generated by
`overlay/apply.mjs` and combines `upstream/` with the rebrand overlay in
`overlay/`. The transformation rules are visible and auditable in
`overlay/replacements.json` and `overlay/files/`.

